RUN 
Type "make" IN Projects/src directory

THE MODEL
This project models a furnitureless room with animated objects in it. There is a planar serial chain manipulator and a humanoid.

ANIMATIONS
Solutions to the animation problem are found by the least squares problem. I used the Dampled leasts squares with dynamically varrying lambda parameter.


USER INTERACTION
Animations, motion and screen capture are enabled by pressing/toggling the folllowing keys.

	drag mouse in inverse kinematics mode to move effectors (light green)
	1,2,3 Selects the models
	esc	= Exit
	space = toggle Inverse an Forward kinematics.
	+/-	= Rotate selected object in Forward Kinmatics mode.
   	r	= (toggle) Screen capture.
   	w	= Move Forward
	s	= Move Backward
	d	= Move right
	a	= Move left
	
	
